title: Quake 4 With Lic- (For Virtual Disc) Lic- is in the description
description:
Leave the two files in the same folder and mount the .cue file (1kb) with your virtual disc.

When the image is mounted, double click the setup.exe file in the virtual disc folder.

- Quake 4 -
- Li----- = DHGR - WFPR - XWGP - KN9P - JWHH

If it tells you to insert the DVD the first time it runs, then close it and start from the desktop shortcut or start/all programs shortcut and it should work fine.
(I'm using Daemon Tools and that works fine)

Please give some feedback, and seed.

PS. I don't know if it works for DVD burning.
